loader = mock.Mock()
facade = staticconf.ConfigFacade.load(self.file.name, self.namespace, loader)
assert_equal(loader.call_count, 1)
time.sleep(1)
facade.reload_if_changed()
assert_equal(loader.call_count, 1)
os.utime(self.file.name, None)
facade.reload_if_changed()
assert_equal(loader.call_count, 2)
